  "content": "e: 14px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 6px; line-height: 1.5;\">Probe hardware<br>auto-assign GPUs</div>\n      <div style=\"position: absolute; top: 50px; left: -2px; width: 50%; height: 3px; background: var(--border);\"></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <!-- What the dev gets -->\n  <div style=\"display: flex; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n    <div style=\"flex: 1; background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 16px; padding: 24px; text-align: center;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 40px; margin-bottom: 8px;\">&#128396;</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700;\">NVIDIA passed through</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 4px;\">nvidia-smi detected</div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"flex: 1; background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 16px; padding: 24px; text-align: center;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 40px; margin-bottom: 8px;\">&#128204;</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700;\">Intel /dev/dri mounted</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 4px;\">render nodes detected</div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"flex: 1; background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 16px; padding: 24px; text-align: center;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 40px; margin-bottom: 8px;\">&#129302;</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700;\"><span class=\"corvia-wm\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">corvia</span> server live</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 4px;\">AI coding assistant gets project memory</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"insight-box\">\n    <p><span class=\"corvia-wm\">corvia</span> is organizational memory for AI agents, and the devcontainer dogfoods it. The AI assistant that helps build <span class=\"corvia-wm\">corvia</span> uses <span class=\"corvia-w